text:
Dear IShowSpeed,

I'm writing to express my sincere gratitude for your recent China trip and the live streams you shared with the world. As a Chinese, I was deeply touched by your genuine exploration of my country.

For a long time, Western media have spread so much misinformation about China that many people around the world have formed inaccurate impressions of us. But you, with your unfiltered live broadcasts, have shattered those false images. You showed the world China's modern cities, high - speed trains with stable network connections even in tunnels, the rich and vibrant street life, and most importantly, the warmth and friendliness of the Chinese people.
